Mister Machine: Death Star

Boilerplate theme for rapid WordPress theme development. Featured include:

1. HTML5 Boilerplate integration
2. Responsive CSS
3. Inclusion of common JavaScript libraries: Modernizr, jQuery UI (tabs, dialog and datepicker), and jQuery Validation
4. Asynchronous Social Widget Scripts for Facebook, Twitter, Google+
5. MailChimp API class
6. Capistrano Deployment script


To Use:

1. Set your environment configuration in wp-config.php. Don't forget to get a new set of Authentication Unique Keys and Salts and adjust your table_prefix as needed.
2. Add an environment trigger file one directory above your project: "env_local", "env_test", etc.
3. For Capistrano deployment, add your deployment settings to /config/deploy.rb
